"The Central Bank of Somalia issued today Mobile Money licence to Hormuud Telecom under the provision of mobile money service within the Federal Republic of Somalia," Abdirahman Abdullahi Mohamed, the CBS governor said in a statement issued on Saturday evening. 

"In formalising our existing digital payments infrastructure, we are accelerating the integration of Somalia's financial system into the global economy," Mr Mohamed added. 



